snippet.title: Yuoni - International Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1444410/Yuoni/
Play a deadly game of hide-and-seek in Yuoni, the new Japanese horror title coming to PlayStation 4 and 5, Steam and Xbox, from August 19th 2021.
